          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.In the Oxygen Data Only the Group of",
                "States Near 6 MeV Appeared with Enough Strengh to",
                "Yield Reliable Results For the Cross Section.We Fit All",
                "These Data with a Sum of Two Gaussian Shaped Peaks,the",
                "Width and Position of the Peak For the 6-MeV Group was",
                "Allowed to Vary,Whereas the Width of the Elastic Peak",
                "Was Fixed As Determined by the Spectrometer Resolution",
                "Except For Slight Broadening Due to Kinematic Effects.",
                "Other States in O-16 and Reactions Such As P,2P and P,",
                "Pd Contribute to a Background That Lies Partly Beneath",
                "The 6-7 MeV Group.To Subtract this Contribution We Used",
                "A Background Function,Which had a Threshold 7 MeV Below",
                "The Elastic Peak.This Background Affects the Area",
                "Assigned to the 6-MeV Group by Less Than 10%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ENDBIB": {
